00:04:16,250 --> 00:04:18,550
that are successful on other platforms,

98
00:04:18,551 --> 00:04:20,449
then you take a look at the Windows store

99
00:04:20,450 --> 00:04:22,829
and ask, "Of the apps that are available

100
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:24,269
"to do sort of the same thing,

101
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:26,609
"are there any features that they're missing?"

102
00:04:26,610 --> 00:04:28,789
Think about how you can introduce apps

103
00:04:28,790 --> 00:04:31,609
that work great on any Windows 10 device,

104
00:04:31,610 --> 00:04:35,309
and the benefits to having the user of those apps

105
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:37,969
work across an ecosystem of Windows 10 devices.

106
00:04:37,970 --> 00:04:40,990
Not just one specific, either desktop or phone, app.

107
00:04:40,991 --> 00:04:45,069
Think about how you could add Cortana integration,

108
00:04:45,070 --> 00:04:47,249
in order to enhance the experience.

109
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:50,509
Think about live tiles, and how you can use those,

110
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:53,489
periodically updating the content on those tiles,

111
00:04:53,490 --> 00:04:55,749
in order to inform the user

112
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:58,899
without them having to explode the application open.

113
00:04:59,330 --> 00:05:01,289
And just think about how you can

114
00:05:01,290 --> 00:05:03,269
improve the user's experience.

115
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:05,629
